<% content_for :jumbotron do %>
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Simple pricing with no surprises</h1>
    <p class="lead">All plans include a 30 day free trial. No credit card required.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid marketing">
    <div class="tab-pane">
      <div class="price-table price-table-three">
        <div class="price-column  price-column-first">
          <%= render partial: 'plan', object: @plans[:small] %>
        </div>
        <div class="price-column price-column-featured">
          <%= render partial: 'plan', object: @plans[:medium] %>
        </div>
        <div class="price-column  price-column-last">
          <%= render partial: 'plan', object: @plans[:large] %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>

<div class="row-fluid marketing">
  <center>
    <h2>Free for Public Projects</h2>
    <p class="lead">Create as free <strong>Public Projects</strong> on any plan and we won't charge you a cent! Perfect for companies that champion their own open source projects.</p>
      <%= link_to 'Start your free trial', new_registration_path(:user), class: "btn btn-large" %>
  </center>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="row-fluid marketing">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6">
        <h4>Is my content safe and secure?</h4>
        <p>Absolutely! All your content is backed up hourly, encrypted and stored. Traffic to/from our servers is encrtyped using SSL, the same as banks use.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <h4>How does the Free Trial work?</h4>
        <p>When you sign up for a trial account you get access to all of Conductors features. This allows you to explore the product and use it with your team. Once the trial period ends you can pick a plan that suits your needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6">
        <h4>Can I change my plan at any time?</h4>
        <p>Yes you can, plans can be upgraded or downgraded at any time. Click on the "Billing" link in your dashboard to see your options.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <h4>Can I get a refund?</h4>
        <p>If you decide to cancel your account, you won't be charged again, but you are responsible for whatever charges have already been incurred for the current billing period.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6">
        <h4>Will I be charged if cancel before my trial expires?</h4>
        <p>If you cancel your account within the 30 day trial period we wont bill you anything.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <h4>Do you offer discounts?</h4>
        <p>Yes. You can get 15% off when you sign up for a year or more.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

